@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rrhwwz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((tmp * (v2 + 0.85 * tmp + 0.59)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.sin(v0 + 0.08) - (tmp + 0.79 + v2 + 0.46)))
    v0 = 0.59
    v1 = wp.cos((tmp + (v1 + 0.30 / v2 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
